        <Parent_String>wind catchers [300248183], ventilation towers [300451356], towers (building divisions) [300003615], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
